---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';

const today = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { weekday: 'long', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' });
---
<BaseLayout title="Leo Daily Horoscope · cusprose" path="/horoscopes/leo/" description="Today's horoscope for Leo — written, not generated. Updated daily.">
  <Nav current="Horoscopes" />

  <main class="sign-page">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="crumb">HOROSCOPES / LEO</p>

      <header class="head">
        <span class="glyph" aria-hidden="true">♌</span>
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow"><span class="star">✦</span> FIRE · FIXED · SUN</p>
          <h1>Leo.</h1>
          <p class="dates">July 23 – August 22</p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="grid">
        <article class="reading">
          <p class="date-label">TODAY · {today}</p>
          <blockquote>
            "Being seen and being known aren't the same.<br/>Today, let someone close enough to do the second."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="body">
            The Sun lights your fifth house today, and the urge to create — to make something with your name on it —
            runs warm. Leo doesn't perform for approval the way people assume; you generate heat and want it to land
            somewhere real. Pour it into the work, not the reaction. The applause is a side effect, never the point.
          </p>
          <p class="body">
            Pride may tempt you to handle alone what would be lighter shared. Asking isn't a loss of standing. Around
            evening, a small act of generosity returns to you in a form you didn't predict. Stay open to the shape of it.
          </p>

          <div class="ratings">
            <div><p class="r-label">LOVE</p><p class="r-stars">★★★★☆</p></div>
            <div><p class="r-label">WORK</p><p class="r-stars">★★★★☆</p></div>
            <div><p class="r-label">MONEY</p><p class="r-stars">★★★★★</p></div>
            <div><p class="r-label">MOOD</p><p class="r-stars">★★★★☆</p></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="side">
          <div class="panel">
            <p class="p-head">JUMP TO</p>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/horoscopes/leo/">Today</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">This week</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">This month</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">2026 yearly</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <p class="p-head">PAIRS WELL WITH</p>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/compatibility/">Aries &times; Leo</a></li>
              <li><a href="/compatibility/">Sagittarius &times; Leo</a></li>
              <li><a href="/tarot/the-star/">Strength card</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sign-page { padding-bottom: 6rem; }
  .crumb { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .head .glyph { font-size: 4.5rem; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .eyebrow .star { color: var(--gold); margin-right: 0.4rem; }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1; }
  .dates { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-top: 0.3rem; }

  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; align-items: start; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .reading {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
    border-radius: 22px;
    padding: 2rem 2.2rem;
  }
  .date-label { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  blockquote { font-size: 1.35rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.35; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .body { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }

  .ratings { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(22,24,58,0.1); }
  .r-label { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .r-stars { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  .side { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }
  .panel { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--surface-border); border-radius: 18px; padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem; }
  .p-head { font-size: 0.66rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .panel ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.55rem; }
  .panel a { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--ink); border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.18s; }
  .panel a:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }
</style>
